<h1 id="tooltipster">Tooltipster</h1>

<p>A flexible and extensible jQuery plugin for modern tooltips by Caleb Jacob and Louis Ameline under MIT license.<br />
Compatible with Mozilla Firefox, Google Chrome, IE6+ and others.<br />
Requires jQuery 1.10+ (or less, see the compatibility note in the doc).<br />
Default css + js files = 10Kb gzipped.</p>

<p>A reminder of options/methods lies below. For detailed documentation, visit http://iamceege.github.io/tooltipster/</p>

